5. div and span tag - to group things together
<div> is a block level generic container, just like <h1> will create a new line
<span> is a inline group container


6.Attributes (adding additional information to tags)
(key = value)
<src>
<img src = "xxxx.png">  -- for images
<a href = > --for hyperlink
<a href="url">Link text</a>
#<a href="weather.html">go to weather page</a> 也可以是local的网页，但是还是在引号里


7.HTML table
<table border = "1">
	<tr> <!-- tr for each row -->
		<th>name</th> <!-- th for table head -->
		<th>age</th> 
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>carol</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>22</td>
	</tr>
</table>

---other way no difference in appearance,dintingish for browswer stuff
<table border = "1">
<thead>
	<tr> <!-- tr for each row -->
		<th>name</th> <!-- th for table head -->
		<th>age</th> 
	</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
	<tr>
		<td>carol</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>22</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Kate</td> <!-- td for each cell -->
		<td>23</td>
	</tr>
</tbody>
</table>


8.HTML forms
<form> is like a container
-action : the url to send form data to
-method: the type of HTTP request
method :"get" for retriving data, such as searching, not change things in database ; "post" to add it to a data base

<input> what to put in the box

<h1>Sign In</h1>

<form action="/sign-in-url" method = "post">
	<input type="text" name="">
	<input type="password" name="">
	<button>Login</button>
</form>

<form> is also a block tag

9.HTML label
use for and id ,if there are matched then can knock them down (connect them)


10. form validations
(check if your input is follow the requirement)
加上required --- 存在的要求！不能提交空表格
can also check if it is a email, etc, certain specifc requirement

<input type="radio" name=""> <!-- only one choice -->
<input type="checkbox" name="">  <!-- can check it or not -->


<form> <!-- 给same name 就可以只选择一个了 -->
	<label for = "dogs"> Dogs:</label>
	<input id = "dogs" type="radio" name="petChoice"
	value="DOGS">
	<label for = "cats"> Cats:</label>
	<input id = "cats" type="radio" name="petChoice"
	value="CATS">
  <p>what's your favorite food </p>
	<select name = "food">  //要有name在上面才能显示提交的改变，value确定的是返回值
		<option>rice</option>
		<option>ramen</option>
	</select>
	<button>Check！</button> <!-- 如果button是最后一个的话会自动提交 -->
</form>








